OL,3,CCumbria Police officers awarded for
OL,4,Cbravery following 'violent' knife
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FTwo Cumbria Police officers have been
OL,8,Fhonoured at the National Police
OL,9,FBravery Awards for their actions
OL,10,Fduring a 'brutal' knife attack.
OL,12,FPCs Heather Watson and Matthew
OL,13,FJohnston are said to have displayed
OL,14,F'extraordinary courage,
OL,15,Fprofessionalism, and dedication to
OL,16,Fprotecting the public' in what's
OL,17,Fdescribed as a 'violent' and
OL,18,F'unprovoked' assault, in which PC
OL,19,FWatson was injured.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
