FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1784047673
OL,3,CCumbria Police officers awarded for
OL,4,Cbravery following 'violent' knife
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FThe incident took place at an address
OL,8,Fin Carlisle in May 2025 where the
OL,9,Fpair, after responding to a call from
OL,10,Fa 'vulnerable victim', were subjected
OL,11,Fto an unprovoked attack by a woman
OL,12,Farmed with a hunting knife.
OL,14,FDuring the incident, PC Watson
OL,15,Fsustained a serious injury to her face.
OL,17,FDespite this, she continued to work
OL,18,Falongside PC Johnston to bring the
OL,19,Fsituation under control and protect
OL,20,Fothers from harm.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1784047673
OL,3,CCumbria Police officers awarded for
OL,4,Cbravery following 'violent' knife
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FTheir actions have been widely praised
OL,8,Fand the officers were recognised
OL,9,Fnationally by the Police Federation at
OL,10,Fthe National Police Bravery Awards
OL,11,Fheld in London on 9 July, where they
OL,12,Freceived the North West regional award.
OL,14,F"This award is thoroughly deserved and
OL,15,Freflects the outstanding courage,
OL,16,Fprofessionalism and resilience shown
OL,17,Fby Heather and Matt in exceptionally
OL,18,Fdifficult circumstances," said Chief
OL,19,FConstable Darren Martland.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
