OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1784047673
OL,3,CCumbria Police officers awarded for
OL,4,Cbravery following 'violent' knife
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"While carrying out their duties and
OL,8,Fsupporting a vulnerable victim, they
OL,9,Fwere subjected to a brutal and
OL,10,Funexpected attack. Despite the danger
OL,11,Fthey faced, they remained focused on
OL,12,Fprotecting one another and
OL,13,Fsafeguarding the public.
OL,15,F"Everyone across Cumbria Constabulary
OL,16,Fis immensely proud of their actions
OL,17,Fand this national recognition."
OL,19,FDavid Allen, Cumbria's Police, Fire
OL,20,Fand Crime Commissioner said 'they
OL,21,Frepresent the very best of policing.'
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUyD@_O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
