PN,32905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1784047673
OL,3,CCumbria Police officers awarded for
OL,4,Cbravery following 'violent' knife
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"Heather and Matt displayed
OL,8,Fexceptional courage, professionalism
OL,9,Fand resilience in the most challenging
OL,10,Fcircumstances," he said.
OL,12,F"While simply coming to work to
OL,13,Fprotect and serve the public, they
OL,14,Fsuffered injuries themselves during a
OL,15,Fviolent attack. Despite that, they
OL,16,Fremained focused on protecting others
OL,17,Fand bringing the situation under
OL,18,Fcontrol.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
