OL,3,CCumbria Police officers awarded for
OL,4,Cbravery following 'violent' knife
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"They represent the very best of
OL,8,Fpolicing and this national recognition
OL,9,Fis thoroughly deserved. Cumbria is
OL,10,Fincredibly proud of them both."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
